                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/976ef4f4-2025-11e2-af16-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/976ef4f4-2025-11e2-af16-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test node-provisioning_1 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Failed to provision nodes: lustre-master-el6-x86_64-sles11sp2-x86_64 #999: Node provisioning timed out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Provision failed for SLES11 SP2&lt;br/&gt;
Info required for matching: node-provisioning-1 node-provisioning_1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
